He denies having any knowledge of the great Gupta plan. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Former Eskom CEO, Brian Molefe refused to comment about allegations related to the Guptas and the removal of Nhlanhla Nene. Molefe denies having any knowledge of the great Gupta plan. WATCH: Zondo Commission hears more Eskom-related testimony He is testifying at the State Capture Inquiry on Eskom-related testimony.